    "Though Bony never supervised a British dissertation, his influence on English medievalist art-historians was significant, largely his <em>Chartes</em>-style training (Kidson).": [],
    "Bony's focus was (again, in Kidson's estimation) on \"how the artistic imagination manifested itself in the work of particular architects.\"": [
        [
            28,
            34,
            [
                "Kid son",
                "Kids on"
            ]
        ]
